{"tid":1839721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我求下醫護人員立即罷工","createTime":"2020-01-24T14:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T14:37:26.000Z","uid":3358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9430e799d0643449d38581986b16c16e232cf4a8","tid":1839721,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"疫情有幾嚴重我諗大家都知道<br />\n但礙於醫德問題一眾醫護人員唔可以離開崗位<br />\n但而家各大tg都傳緊要抽生死簽<br />\n我都相信係真<br />\n政府無止境咁放毒入黎<br />\n前線既醫護人員根本同送頭無分別<br />\n<br />\n而家呢一刻唔再係分藍黃既時候<br />\n因為個病毒唔會因為你政見而選擇唔感染你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我認我自私，但為左香港人為左全體醫護人員既生命安危，我求下你地立即罷工去逼使呢個無能既政府去做野，我真係唔想咁樣死，亦都唔想香港人因為政府既無能而病死</span></span>"},{"pid":"e83f110e49b5424c8331f17d8708308c8d27c81e","tid":1839721,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"beea5e3ddfe8220fca8863669ea04d8c27178a52","tid":1839721,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下醫護人員立即罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecd5bdfee61b533d4dc8409b1d10bffb4147483c","tid":1839721,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下醫護人員立即罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"af1dfc33ef0147a10f820a1c00759328b5ddb068","tid":1839721,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:2